title: At age 55 and after 150 buildings, 'French spiderman' keeps climbing
text:
At age 55 and after 150 buildings, 'French spiderman' keeps climbing 5:16pm IST - 01:27 
Alain Robert, dubbed the 'French Spiderman' scales the fourth-tallest building in the Paris business district, Tour Total, in roughly an hour. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
